Second Department,

June, 1958

(June 2, 1958) Lillian Block, Appellant, v. Joseph H. Breindel, Respondent.

Motion referred to the court that rendered the decision. Present — Nolan, P. J., Beldock, Murphy, Ughetta and Hallinan, JJ. Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Murphy, Hallinan and Kleinfeld, JJ.
